OL,8,Fa rare condition that attacked his
OL,9,Fnervous system says he owes his life
OL,10,Fto people who donated their plasma.
OL,12,FMark Hobbs, from Cowplain, in
OL,13,FHampshire, was struck down with an
OL,14,Fautoimmune disorder that paralysed
OL,15,Fhis entire body in a matter of hours.
OL,17,F"I was in ICU on full life support by
OL,18,F10 o'clock that night - I went
OL,19,Fdownhill within hours," he said.
